title: Deaths of British tourists abroad 2009 to 2014
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of deaths, containing a total of 5 data points.
In general Number of deaths has fallen over the Year.
Number of deaths is roughly constant from 2009/2010 to 2012/2013, and finally slightly decreasing from 2012/2013 to 2013/2014.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2012/2013 and 2013/2014.
Maximum Number of deaths, about 6237.0 was reported at Year 2011/2012
Minimum Number of deaths about 4110.0 was reached at Year 2013/2014
